{"tid":350183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地撐高圖爾斯︰佢係最佳劊子手","createTime":"2017-08-07T05:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T08:30:56.000Z","uid":10199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e886f10205ac51b4e98b547cbae96253f92fb83","tid":350183,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"車路士在周日不敵阿仙奴失落社區盾，罪人之一肯定是有份主射12碼的門將高圖爾斯，不過領隊干地力撐他是陣中其中一位最出色劊子手，絕不後悔找他主射12碼。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴射贏12碼捧社區盾<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯令人意外地成為5位主射極刑的其中一人，但他的射門一飛衝天，加上前鋒莫拉達亦射失，令車仔失落錦標，干地說︰「高圖爾斯在訓練中證實他是其中一位最佳劊子手，選他踢絕對正確，不要忘記莫拉達是前鋒一樣會射失。」<br />\n<br />\n同時間，干地同意莫拉達今場表現未達預期︰「他仍需付出更多努力，畢竟只與我們練習了一星期，體能和足球理念是很重要一環，這對魯迪格和巴卡約高也一樣。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=8kwyYxWn41c2N58G8jocGZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7ba5186d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"5545cf03f6feb4ca1c434bd3fca339939a697af0","tid":350183,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"聽得20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54698258d994fc37d3061049430df67b7c9f159c","tid":350183,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踢得20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"185567a2fbd651747d665745473439f9bd488de1","tid":350183,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor